# 138 Boitelo Bo Tletsen.

 Nka bophelo ba ka, U ntokisetse ba Hau;U nke ’tsoho la ka Le etse thato ea Hau.   
CHORUSNtlhatsoe maling a Konyana (a Konyana)Ntlhatsoe maling a Konyana (a Konyana)Ntlhatsoe mohloling (mohloling)   
Nkuke Morena E be ka ho sa eng kae.Nka maoto a ka, A mathele ho Uena   
Nka ’ntsoe la ka kamehla, Ke tle ke U binele.Nka molomo oa ka, O tlale mantsoe a Hao;   
U nke hohle ha ka ’Me ho se sale letho.Nka nako tsa ka tsohle, Li U rorise joalo;   
Nka kelello ea ka U e sebelise eohe.Inkele thato ea ka, E be ee U e ratang;   
Inkele pelo ea ka E be ee U e ratang;Inkele pelo ea ka E be eona tolo ea Hao.   
Nka rato la ka Jesu, Le beoa matong a Hao;U nkuke hohle ha ka, Ke be oa Hao kamehla.
